  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Hybrid Working Arrangement</li>\n  <li>Great Working Environment and Team Culture</li>\n  <li>Centrally Located</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Job Description &amp; Requirements</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and map out solution providers in your target market</li>\n  <li>Contact that market through calls and meetings.</li>\n  <li>Build strong relationships through your market intelligence and strong client delivery to grow your events</li>\n  <li>Have a deep understanding of your clients' business objectives to make your event an integral part of the development strategy</li>\n  <li>Creative unique package development to suit your clients objectives through conferences and an online platform</li>\n  <li>Create in depth proposals that meet all the clients objectives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Ideal Candidate:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Accumulated good sales experience in Conferences, Events, Advertising, Media or Market Research</li>\n  <li>B2B sales exeperience</li>\n  <li>Analytical personality</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Strong drive to succeed</li>\n  <li>Good team player</li>\n</ul>",
