    "uen": "199702288Z",
    "description": "<p>   IQPC is an international events business that specializes in the production, sales and delivery of B2B C-Level Conferences. Based in Robinson Road, our Singapore office is populated by a cosmopolitan mixture of multilingual and talented professionals. The office is active in most industry sectors, but particularly prominent in Shared Services and Finance, Infrastructure, Oil and Gas and Defence.</p>  <p>   Fast paced, young and dynamic we promote a ‘work hard, play hard’ culture where employees are supported, developed and recognised for their contributions both as individuals and teams. </p>  <p>   <em>“Identifying, developing and retaining talented staff is key to our success. The conference business is like no other environment, the pace and intensity is high but so are the rewards. Supporting our staff through training and incentives programs, plus promoting an inclusive and dynamic culture makes this an exciting place to work”.  </em></p>  <p>   <em>Liz Ong, Country Manager Singapore</em></p>  ",
